程序包 aquintos.ee.metric.temp.calc.B_Team_Dev.VCUtil

类 VCUtil.WriteInfoView

  • java.lang.Object
    • aquintos.ee.metric.temp.calc.B_Team_Dev.VCUtil.VCUtil.WriteInfoView
  • 封闭类:
    VCUtil
    public static class VCUtil.WriteInfoView
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility class for writing information to the InfoView with or without ITempTable data.

    Example Usage: 

     
 // Example 1: Writing information based on some object
 VCUtil.WriteInfoViewByITempTable.WriteInfoViewByObject("InfoEntryName", someObject, LogLevel.INFO);

 // Example 2: Writing information based on ITempTables
 String[] tableNames = {"Sheet1", "Sheet2", "Sheet3"};
 ITempTable[] tables = {tempTable1, tempTable2, tempTable3};
 VCUtil.WriteInfoViewByITempTable.WriteInfoViewByITempTable("MultipleTablesInfo", tableNames, tables, LogLevel.WARNING, 2);

 // Example 3: Writing information based on one single ITempTable
 VCUtil.WriteInfoViewBySingleITempTable("SingleTablesInfo", table, LogLevel.WARNING, 2);
